719313f-a.title: Manhattan: Division Street - Market Street
719313f-a.text:
Division Street, west from but not including Market Street.
The view is taken from the Manhattan Bridge.
September 24, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
The same, at a later date, showing the skeleton of the U.S.
Court House in the background.
March 9, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
